                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-28-off157 t18300708-28-cd158"></join>, 1 coat, value 1l.; 1 waistcoat, value 10s.; 1 pair of trousers, value 10s.; 1 seal, value 6d., and 1 handkerchief, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
