                     <interp inst="t18300708-28-person286" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a shopman to Mr. Levy. I have a pair of trousers, which were brought by a young man; he was there but a few minutes - the prisoner does not look like the same man, he is not dressed the same; I think he is not the man - he had not this coat on; I was examined, but the prisoner was not there.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
